Ikechukwu Oke, a student of Ebonyi State University, Abakaliki, has been rushed to the hospital after fasting and praying for 41 days and nights in his room at British lodge. It was gathered that Oke decided to embark on fasting as a result of family challenges and worldly afflictions. One Hon Engr Peter Edeh and others are said to have rushed him to the Accident and Emergency Ward of the Federal Teaching Hospital, FETHA 1, Abakaliki. Source